items.title: Goettl gives gift of cool air to Arizona Animal Welfare League
items.summary:
With the donation of a new air conditioning unit, HVAC entrepreneur Ken Goodrich and his team at Goettl Air Conditioning gave the gift of cool air to the Arizona Animal Welfare League giving the shelter’s dogs, cats and staff ongoing respite from the desert heat.   The AC unit donation is part of a larger renovation and remodel at the AAWL’s central Phoenix location. The nonprofit AAWL is Arizona’s oldest and largest no-kill shelter. “We!
